\b \cf0 Learning
\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\fi720

\fs28 \cf0 - The desire to learn is an important part of Black Crown. There will concepts and items that people may never have heard of, and at the end of the game, they will not have any mechanical improvement, but instead an improvement of the mind. I wish to encourage people to seek out links to learn more about the things that inspired the project. Things such as the Khan Institute, TED, Wikipedia, iTunes U, and other services, can embed nicely or lead people to further their knowledge on certain subjects. 
\fs24 \

\fs28 \
